326
00:29:20,292 --> 00:29:21,208
Xin lỗi!

327
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:25,208
Mẹ ơi, con muốn ăn kem nữa!

328
00:29:25,667 --> 00:29:26,875
Cẩn thận đấy!

329
00:29:28,625 --> 00:29:30,167
