334
00:29:59,083 --> 00:30:00,542
Con làm sao vậy?

335
00:30:08,333 --> 00:30:09,625
KM!

336
00:30:13,833 --> 00:30:15,500
Chào chú! Buổi sáng tốt lành!

337
00:30:49,417 --> 00:30:50,583
Kunal!

338
00:30:52,958 --> 00:30:54,958
